<package version="1.0">
  <name>Numbers_Words</name>
  <summary>The PEAR Numbers_Words package provides methods for spelling numerals in words.</summary>
  <description>With Numbers_Words class you can convert numbers written in
         arabic digits to words in several languages. You can convert an
         integer between -infinity and infinity. If your system does not
         support such long numbers you can call Numbers_Words::toWords()
         with just a string.</description>
